	<name>Trivia</name>
	<summary>A fun quiz game</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			Trivia is a fun quiz game.
		</p>
		<p>
			You can play a quick game composed of 10 random questions or customize your experience with several categories, three levels of difficulty, true/false or multiple choice questions, and between 1 and 50 questions in a game.
		</p>
		<p>
			Check your statistics and try to improve over the time!
		</p>
	</description>
